[
    {
        "text": "Hello, welcome to Michael's Business Top Tips!",
        "startTime": 67,
        "endTime": 3117,
        "slowStartTime": 250,
        "slowEndTime": 4900
    },
    {
        "text": "This month, we're looking at leadership versus management.",
        "startTime": 3600,
        "endTime": 6517,
        "slowStartTime": 5550,
        "slowEndTime": 10000
    },
    {
        "text": "What does this mean?",
        "startTime": 7233,
        "endTime": 8050,
        "slowStartTime": 11000,
        "slowEndTime": 12300
    },
    {
        "text": "An expert in this field is a gentleman called John Kotter...",
        "startTime": 8633,
        "endTime": 11850,
        "slowStartTime": 13100,
        "slowEndTime": 18000
    },
    {
        "text": "...who's a professor of leadership at Harvard Business School.",
        "startTime": 12167,
        "endTime": 14650,
        "slowStartTime": 18400,
        "slowEndTime": 22200
    },
    {
        "text": "He argues that management is focused very much on complexity,...",
        "startTime": 15500,
        "endTime": 18917,
        "slowStartTime": 23400,
        "slowEndTime": 28600
    },
    {
        "text": "...dealing with the complex daily routines such as budgeting, organizing, problem solving, etc.",
        "startTime": 19533,
        "endTime": 25403,
        "slowStartTime": 29450,
        "slowEndTime": 38330
    },
    {
        "text": "All very important, but not leadership.",
        "startTime": 26067,
        "endTime": 29583,
        "slowStartTime": 39250,
        "slowEndTime": 44600
    },
    {
        "text": "John Kotter says leadership is to deal with change,...",
        "startTime": 30300,
        "endTime": 33317,
        "slowStartTime": 45600,
        "slowEndTime": 50200
    },
    {
        "text": "...helping companies grow, develop, and move into new areas.",
        "startTime": 33633,
        "endTime": 37950,
        "slowStartTime": 50600,
        "slowEndTime": 57150
    },
    {
        "text": "He identifies four principles to being a successful leader.",
        "startTime": 39100,
        "endTime": 42517,
        "slowStartTime": 58800,
        "slowEndTime": 64000
    },
    {
        "text": "First, create vision and strategy.",
        "startTime": 43299,
        "endTime": 45317,
        "slowStartTime": 65099,
        "slowEndTime": 68200
    },
    {
        "text": "A leader has a clear vision of where they want to go to and their company to go to,...",
        "startTime": 46233,
        "endTime": 50783,
        "slowStartTime": 69500,
        "slowEndTime": 76400
    },
    {
        "text": "...and strategy sets the map how to get there.",
        "startTime": 51300,
        "endTime": 54850,
        "slowStartTime": 77100,
        "slowEndTime": 82500
    },
    {
        "text": "Second, communicate and set direction.",
        "startTime": 56133,
        "endTime": 59017,
        "slowStartTime": 84350,
        "slowEndTime": 88750
    },
    {
        "text": "A good leader needs to be a good communicator.",
        "startTime": 59867,
        "endTime": 62117,
        "slowStartTime": 89950,
        "slowEndTime": 93400
    },
    {
        "text": "They need to communicate their vision clearly to the people they work with...",
        "startTime": 62900,
        "endTime": 66317,
        "slowStartTime": 94500,
        "slowEndTime": 99700
    },
    {
        "text": "...and also set a clear direction for everybody to move forward.",
        "startTime": 66667,
        "endTime": 70150,
        "slowStartTime": 100150,
        "slowEndTime": 105450
    },
    {
        "text": "Third, motivate action.",
        "startTime": 71433,
        "endTime": 73217,
        "slowStartTime": 107300,
        "slowEndTime": 110050
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, emotion is key.",
        "startTime": 74200,
        "endTime": 75650,
        "slowStartTime": 111450,
        "slowEndTime": 113700
    },
    {
        "text": "A good leader should be using persuasive skills,...",
        "startTime": 76300,
        "endTime": 79865,
        "slowStartTime": 114600,
        "slowEndTime": 120022
    },
    {
        "text": "...inspiring, praising, recognizing the work of others,...",
        "startTime": 80053,
        "endTime": 84317,
        "slowStartTime": 120229,
        "slowEndTime": 126700
    },
    {
        "text": "...to encourage them and motivate them to successful action.",
        "startTime": 84567,
        "endTime": 87783,
        "slowStartTime": 127000,
        "slowEndTime": 131900
    },
    {
        "text": "Finally, align people.",
        "startTime": 88967,
        "endTime": 90517,
        "slowStartTime": 133600,
        "slowEndTime": 136000
    },
    {
        "text": "A good leader needs to make sure everybody is working in the same direction.",
        "startTime": 91133,
        "endTime": 95250,
        "slowStartTime": 136850,
        "slowEndTime": 143100
    },
    {
        "text": "Everybody is aiming at the same goals.",
        "startTime": 95867,
        "endTime": 97917,
        "slowStartTime": 143950,
        "slowEndTime": 147100
    },
    {
        "text": "This is key to success of achieving the vision.",
        "startTime": 98300,
        "endTime": 100617,
        "slowStartTime": 147600,
        "slowEndTime": 151150
    },
    {
        "text": "Now remember, anybody can be a leader.",
        "startTime": 102067,
        "endTime": 105050,
        "slowStartTime": 153250,
        "slowEndTime": 157800
    },
    {
        "text": "It doesn't have to be a manager to be a leader.",
        "startTime": 105700,
        "endTime": 107683,
        "slowStartTime": 158700,
        "slowEndTime": 161750
    },
    {
        "text": "So, use these four principles to become a leader yourself.",
        "startTime": 108333,
        "endTime": 111850,
        "slowStartTime": 162650,
        "slowEndTime": 168000
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you and good luck!",
        "startTime": 112933,
        "endTime": 114150,
        "slowStartTime": 169550,
        "slowEndTime": 171450
    }
]